      "text": "1 Vehicle comes in\n2 Entry Gate will provide ticket\n3 Parking attendant assigns a spot\n4 Vehicle park\n5 Vehicke unpark\n6 Exit Gate will see the ticket and invoice is generated\n7 Payment happens\n8 Spot become free\n\n",
