      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2️⃣ Invoice — WHY it needs status 🧾\n\nWhat Invoice represents\n“This is the bill for parking.”\n\nInvoice lifecycle\nCREATED → PAID → CANCELLED / EXPIRED\n\nWhy status is needed\n\nHas payment already been done?\nShould we allow retry?\nCan we refund?\nIs the bill still valid?\n\nif invoice.status == \"PAID\":\n    block_exit()\n\n\n✅ Invoice represents a financial obligation → MUST have status",
